{"tid":1674541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚Law撚] 申請禁制令禁止警蛆知法犯法","createTime":"2019-10-25T09:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T09:24:57.000Z","uid":331142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce16b853a2d917c377200adab02c52306e0d38c7","tid":1674541,"uid":331142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:20:44.000Z","msg":"佢地一定以為自己啱哂，法庭都企喺佢地嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實示威者 / 香港市民 / 記者身份可唔可以申請禁制令？<br />\n<br />\n要禁嘅野多到數唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 執行私刑<br />\n2. 純粹因為被語言冒犯而制服或拘捕對方<br />\n3. 不合理拒絕展示委任證<br />\n4. 刻意襲擊守法嘅記者、救護員及途人<br />\n5. 故意傷人<br />\n6. 企圖謀殺<br />\n7. 以公務員身分公開批評或支持政府政策<br />\n（8. 冇腦冇良知冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n如果真係諗得過嘅幫手開新post啦<br />\nP牌冇地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c174fd0e65272c9751258f25b10ce41376b88279","tid":1674541,"uid":38666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"之後法官話唔關我事<br />\n現行機制已經處理到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada24bbeab9afea32202c50733ff770939fe151","tid":1674541,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}